title: What Did We Learn in Week 3?
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and Joey Galloway react to some of Week 3's key results, including Penn State's domination of Auburn and Texas A&M's win over Miami. Also, the crew discusses which coaches are already on the hot seat after two head coaches have already been fired this season. Plus, a look at where Appalachian State's Hail Mary ranks among College Football's greatest Hail Mary plays, and the crew discusses the end of one of the longest rivalries in College Football.
